{"about_the_game":"In Stealth Kart, we mix Real-Time Tactics and Fun Racing. Sneak past the policemen's eyes or get into hot pursuits.<br>The green friend has a fast car and needs to get to the goal. One friendly kid might put the enemy into cardboard boxes or hide in one. Another friendly kid has a ramp car, allowing crazy jumps. The third kid has his dad's donut food truck, avoiding suspicion by selling donuts.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Real-Time Tactics meets Racing gameplay: Pick up and play, beat a level in minutes<br></li><li>Later levels are old-school challenging<br></li><li>Four playable characters, all with unique abilities<br></li><li>Local coop option: real-time tactical teamwork<br></li><li>Hide in cardboard boxes, jump over ramps, drive the ramp car, swim, distract policemen with donuts<br></li><li>Cameraderie between a green alien and friendly kids<br></li><li>Vist gramps for a few tips<br></li><li>Longtime motivation: Replay levels with different approaches for medals<br></li><li>Choose your playstyle: Hot pursuits! Or stealthy sneaking. Or making the policemen swim.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838540/extras/little_chase_new_style_500p.gif?t=1664096599\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838540/extras/ramp_jump_500phalf_frames.gif?t=1664096599\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"TWO CAN PLAY THIS GAME","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1838540/e7e621078172474a0adda62c461b18052b008771.jpg"},{"name":"TRIPLE THREAT","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1838540/428333ade2bcb496be22b5a3532a1ada4edd3e1b.jpg"},{"name":"BLUE BOYS BOMB","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1838540/4e8554c3ea2d20f0d3a7fcd429bbe590c5870659.jpg"},{"name":"DONUT BE AFRAID","path":"https://cdn.akama